        "message": "=<h2>Interview Scheduling</h2>\n\n<p>Hello Candidate,</p>\n\n<p>\nCongratulations! You have been shortlisted for the next interview round for the role of:\n</p>\n\n<h3>\n{{ $('Phase2_Interview_Scheduling').item.json[\"role\"] }}\n</h3>\n\n<p>\nPlease find the available interview slots below:\n</p>\n\n<pre>\n{{ $('Generate Interview Slots').item.json[\"slots\"] }}\n</pre>\n\n<p>\nPlease select your preferred slot using the form below:\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSedKCBfcJB7zvurdUhhVZJL1a3wmDbyDp4nAchsuYuUYldnDA/viewform?usp=dialog\">\nSelect The Slot\n</a>\n</p>\n\n<p>\nRegards,<br>\nHR Team\n</p>",
